heats)<br />{{Date|1980-7-28}} (semi-finals and finals)\n|competitors = 22\n|nations = 14\n|win_value = 12.56 {{OlyR|athletics}}\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Vera Komisova]]\n|goldNOC = URS\n|silver = [[Johanna Klier]]\n|silverNOC = GDR\n|bronze = [[Lucyna Langer]]\n|bronzeNOC = POL\n|prev = [[Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 100 metres hurdles|1976]]\n|next = [[Athletics at the 1984 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 100 metres hurdles|1984]]\n}}\n\n{{AthleticsAt1980SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''women's 100 metres hurdles''' at the [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics|1980 Summer Olympics]] in [[Moscow]], [[Soviet Union]] had an entrylist of 22 competitors, with three qualifying heats (22 runners), two semi-finals (16) before the final (8) took place on Monday 28 July 1980.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1980/ATH/womens-100-metres-hurdles.html |title=Athletics at the 1980 Moscow Summer Games: Women's 100 metres Hurdles |accessdate=24 September 2017 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==Final==\n{| border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"5\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"cccccc\"\n!Rank\n!style=\"width: 20em\"|Final\n!style=\"width: 5em\"|Time\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Image:Med 1.png]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vera Komisova]]|URS|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'''12.56'''\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Image:Med 2.png]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Johanna Klier]]|GDR|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'''12.63'''\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Image:Med 3.png]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Lucyna Langer]]|POL|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'''12.65'''\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|4.\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Kerstin Knabe]]|GDR|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'''12.66'''\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|5.\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Gra\u017cyna Rabsztyn]]|POL|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'''12.74'''\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|6.\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Irina Litovchenko]]|URS|1980 Summer}}\n|align=\"center\" |'